Q : What do you undestand by CDD ?
A : CDD stand for Component driven development.CDD is development mathdelogy that is supoort the build proccess.

it is a proccess that build UI from the "Bottom up" by starting at the level of components and ending at the level of pages or screens.

benifits of using CDD is

: focus on developments
: Increase UI coverage
: Build a component library
: parallelize developments.
